{"tid":1133772,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[愛黨國 高度統一]習近平︰一個人不愛國是很丟臉的事","createTime":"2019-05-01T10:27:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T08:05:25.000Z","uid":51620,"like":7,"dislike":96,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"fae8e1cd5d54d9e155280c1ce206a96af48887dc","tid":1133772,"uid":51620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:27:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.stheadline.com/stheadline/inewsmedia/20170629/_2017062915365043840.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.stheadline.com%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20170629%2F_2017062915365043840.jpg&h=a46fa218&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】在北京，人民大會堂舉行紀念五四運動一百周年大會。中共總書記習近平表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">五四運動精神核心是愛國主義</span>，要堅持愛黨和愛社會主義，又指一個人不愛國是很丟臉的事。<br />\n<br />\n今年是五四運動一百周年，人民大會堂舉行紀念活動。中共總書記習近平、中央政治局常委李克強、栗戰書、汪洋、趙樂際、韓正等都有出席。<br />\n<br />\n習近平在會上發表近一小時講話，強調青年要愛國愛黨。他寄語青年要樹立遠大理想，成為社會主義建設者和接班人。<br />\n<br />\n習近平又指五四運動精神的核心是愛國主義，證明要用奮鬥，才可令國家富強。他說，關心及支持青年是全社會的共同責任，黨政機關以至社會都要關心及支持青年發展，給予年輕人更多機會。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=346333&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346333%26refer%3DShare&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgECHJFIlRN37b%2BuZTNWj4Tkw%3D&h=b06c0fc4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Finternational%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D346333%26refer%3DShare&h=4d502ee9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/international/player?newsId=346333&amp;refer=Share</a>"},{"pid":"70f8360fe899f4c1bdb574185a2ad4c6721de331","tid":1133772,"uid":60164,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:28:37.000Z","msg":"明明係尊重同包容<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7df0a32f14dd5c1d0d709ae6d30c7252e24a5972","tid":1133772,"uid":152108,"like":97,"dislike":0,"score":97,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-01T10:29:27.00